## Technical guide

### Base URL

#### Production

```
https://www.myfinance.com/rss/syndication/
```

- Live production content
- No cache

---

### URL structure

#### Standard endpoint

```
GET {base_url}/{feed_name}/{content_source_identifier}
```

#### Query parameters

| Parameter | Required | Value | Description |
|-----------|----------|-------|-------------|
| `type` | false | `"xml"` | Sets `Content-Type` on response to `text/xml; charset=UTF-8` |
| `page` | false | integer | Paginator parameter |
| `from_date` | false | `YYYY-MM-DD` | Pull content from select dates, typically used for backfilling |
| `to_date` | false | `YYYY-MM-DD` | Same as `from_date` |

If `type` isn't set, **`Content-Type` defaults to `application/rss+xml; charset=utf-8`**.

---

### Per page

Feeds default to **20 articles per page**. This is controlled within the feed delivery system and **cannot be modified** on the request.

---

